==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Klamaths
<hw>Kla"maths</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n. pl.</pos>; <sing>sing.
<singw>Klamath</singw></sing> <fld>(Ethnol.)</fld> <def>A collective
name for the Indians of several tribes formerly living along the Klamath
river, in California and Oregon, but now restricted to a reservation at
Klamath Lake; -- called also <altname>Clamets</altname> and
<altname>Hamati</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

